        'content' => '<p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>1. HOW DOES ONLINE STORE WORK?</strong><br><br></span></p><ul class="listUL"><li><span style="font-size: large;">you are looking for goods and add them to the cart;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">you place an order, entering all necessary data;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">you pay for the order;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">we buy goods from Chinese sellers;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">we check goods for compliance with their description;</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">we arrange goods delivery to the buyer.</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: large;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>2. COULD NOT FIND NECESSARY PRODUCT, WHAT TO DO?</strong><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><br>Сontact online store for help if you could not find necessary product you wanted to purchase.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">You can email us, contact us in social networks or use help of website operator. Be sure to specify all characteristics of the product you need or attach its photo when you contact us.<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><br><strong>3. HOW TO FIND OUT YOUR ORDER STATUS?</strong><br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><br>Enter &ldquo;Orders&rdquo; section in your personal account to find out your order status. You will see a table with your orders information there. It has data on status.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">The following order statuses are available:</span></p><ul class="listUL"><li><span style="font-size: large;">Awaiting payment - you should pay the order to start processing it.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">Paid - in process, but not yet bought.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">Ordered - sent by seller, but not received at our warehouse.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">In handling at warehouse - received at the warehouse.</span></li><li><span style="font-size: large;">Cancelled - order of goods is suspended for any reason.</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-size: large;">You can find out more about the order clicking its number.<br><br><img src="https://clip.otcommerce.com/files/ed/7a/Orders.png" alt="" width="1751" height="580" /><br></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: large;"><br><br><br><br>4. DOES THE PHOTO IN THE CARD MEET REAL PRODUCT?<br><br></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">Online store employees check it goods for their compliance with specified characteristics and production defects upon receipt in the warehouse. Goods may be replaced if non-conformity is detected.<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><br>Therefore, you will receive exactly the thing indicated on Chinese seller&rsquo;s photo.<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><br>Important!</strong> Some sellers use professional photographs of their products, so actual colours can be slightly different: lighter or darker.<br><br></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: large;"><br>5. HOW TO TRACK THE PARCEL?<br><br></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">After receiving goods in our warehouse we will provide you a tracking number to track your order delivery.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><br>6. WHY DO I NEED A PERSONAL CUSTOMER&rsquo;S ACCOUNT?<br><br></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">Your personal account stores all necessary information for processing and delivering your orders. Here you can also add funds, check purchase history, trace stages of order execution and clarify information on any order you are interested in.<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><br>You can always change your personal data and contact information.<br><br></span><span style="font-size: large;">Registration on the site will allow you to carry out all subsequent orders much faster. You do not have to fill in delivery details again. They will be automatically taken from your personal account.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><br>7. WHAT IS A CUSTOMER`S PAYMENT ACCOUNT?<br></strong><br>This is your personal customer&rsquo;s account in our online store. You can add funds here and use them to pay for your orders.</span></p><div>&nbsp;</div>',
